{
  "texts": [
    "Now the most important stage in the pipeline is the fusion label.",
    "The 'M-N' label is displayed with a corresponding probability value to confirm the justification for the new label obtained.",
    "The 'M-N' label is a fusion label describing the high possibility of the presence of malignancy in the reported samples and some form of normal classification also.",
    "However, the corresponding probability values justifies that the malignancy is more dominant than the normal label, thereby helping to explain the fusion label.",
    "In this section, a closer examination of the findings from the study is conducted from two perspectives: statistical analysis and comparative analysis of performance of the proposed multimodal neural network with similar state-of-the-art methods."
  ]
}